{
  "stem": "8842.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They would shoot into these four men, and they themselves would fall in over to the other side.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is how they got rid of all the men that were there-- I don't know how many hundreds, or couple of thousand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When my father's turn came to do the same thing, he was already one of the last, last ones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were maybe 30 or 37 people, if I remember he told me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He told us that he had to take, he and another three men, a body and go up the hill.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What I meant is go up the hill-- on the other side was also the same kind of ditch.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Like, they were here-- on the other side of the hill was also like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they just threw all the dead ones there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They picked up that man, that dead man, and they went up the hill, threw them into the other side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And while they had to face now the German or the Lithuanian, one of the Lithuanians looked at my father and he said to him, take off your boots.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I like them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I would like to have them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he sat down and started to take the boots off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, he says, you wear a very good pair-- special pants that they went into the boots like riding pants.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is how he was dressed to escape, if you remember what I told you, yeah?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said to him, all right, before I'm taking out-- giving you back my pants, too, let me just tell you what I have in my pocket that you should know.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That you are going to kill now a man that was fighting for the independence of [INAUDIBLE] Lithuania, which my father was.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
